sub_title: MSc Biomedicine I Medical Information and Adverse Event Intake Specialist
summary:
Operations Specialist covering areas of Medical Information and Adverse Event Intake for the German-speaking market at IQVIA in Zagreb, Croatia.

I obtained my Master's in Medical science with a major in Biomedicine and Life Science Industry Research specialization at Lund University, Sweden. Prior to that I have completed my BSc Biomedical Sciences at Maastricht University, The Netherlands.

I am an ambitious individual with knowledge of various therapeutic areas, striving to aid and improve health across various domains. As I have lived in several countries, I have a lot of experience in international study and work environments. 

Happy to connect!
